code: import axios from'axios';const API_URL=`${process.env.REACT_APP_API_URL}/api/notes`;export const getNotes=()=>axios.get(API_URL);export const getNoteById=id=>axios.get(`${API_URL}/${id}`);export const createNote=noteData=>axios.post(API_URL,noteData);export const updateNote=(id,updatedData)=>axios.put(`${API_URL}/${id}`,updatedData);export const deleteNote=id=>axios.delete(`${API_URL}/${id}`);export const submitNoteForApproval=id=>axios.patch(`${API_URL}/${id}/submit`);
